WEBVTT

00:01:00.253 --> 00:01:02.240
But to his surprise,

00:01:02.264 --> 00:01:05.128
the composite portrait that he produces

00:01:05.951 --> 00:01:07.207
is beautiful.

00:01:10.026 --> 00:01:13.054
Galton's surprising finding
raises deep questions:

00:01:13.515 --> 00:01:15.100
What is beauty?

00:01:16.070 --> 00:01:22.889
Why do certain configurations of line
and color and form excite us so?

00:01:24.372 --> 00:01:25.900
For most of human history,

00:01:25.924 --> 00:01:31.479
these questions have been approached
using logic and speculation.